    "Name": "Álfar",
    "Details": "The Álfar AL-A1 fielded an impressive amount of firepower for its size. A PPC mounted on its right arm was the main weapon. Three medium lasers, two on the left arm and one in the head, plus a SRM-6 missile rack with 1 ton of ammo, all in the left shoulder, provided ample backup and close-range punch. Fifteen heat sinks provided good battlefield endurance.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Nimble</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.03</color></b>",
